---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="BRICS Brokers - BRICS Investment & Finance News"
  description="Latest news on BRICS investments, de-dollarization, new BRICS currency, and emerging market opportunities for global investors."
  lang="en"
>
  <Fragment slot="logo">BRICS Brokers</Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="footer-name">BRICS Brokers</Fragment>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>BRICS Investment & Finance Hub</h1>
    <p>Your trusted source for BRICS economic news, de-dollarization trends, and emerging market investment opportunities.</p>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h2>BRICS Currency 2026</h2>
      <p>The new BRICS common currency initiative is reshaping global finance. Learn about BRICS Pay, digital currencies, and what it means for investors worldwide.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>De-Dollarization Trends</h2>
      <p>China and Russia push for alternatives to the US dollar. Analysis of yuan internationalization, new swap lines, and the impact on global trade.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>New Development Bank</h2>
      <p>With $42.9 billion approved across 139 projects, the NDB is financing infrastructure across emerging economies. Explore the latest funded projects.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Emerging Market Opportunities</h2>
      <p>Investment opportunities in Brazil, India, China, South Africa, and new BRICS+ member nations. Sector analysis and market forecasts.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>BRICS Summit 2026</h2>
      <p>The 18th BRICS Summit in New Delhi (September 2026) will shape the future of multilateral cooperation. Key agenda items and expected outcomes.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Intra-BRICS Trade</h2>
      <p>Intra-BRICS trade reached $1.17 trillion. Discover the fastest-growing trade corridors and sectors driving South-South commerce.</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>
</BaseLayout>
